Package de.unibayreuth.bayceer.bayeos.xmlrpc.handler.inf Description

Provides the interface classes necessary to access the xml-rpc handlers All handler interfaces are defined by this package. There are secured and unsecured handlers. Secured handler use http authentication. The handler name can be calculated by the interface name omitting the first character.

e.g. ILoginHandler -> LoginHandler
Since:
1.6.5
Author:
Oliver Archner
